Date: Tue, 08 Sep 1998 08:18:06 -0400
From: Stan Cope <COPES@nehc.med.navy.mil>

At the risk of being accused of splitting hairs, let us remember that
mosquitoes transmit pathogens (sensu latu) and not diseases.
